# FitPDF Environment Variables
# 
# IMPORTANT: Add these in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# 1. NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID - Get from analytics.google.com
# 2. NEXT_PUBLIC_URL - Your Vercel app URL
#
# Example values below - replace with your actual values:

NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
NEXT_PUBLIC_URL=https://fitpdf-mu.vercel.app